    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1StackLayoutParams" kindref="compound">StackLayoutParams</ref> stores per-child layout parameters for <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1StackLayout" kindref="compound">StackLayout</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This handle provides direct access to the layout weight attached to a child view. Use <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View_1a772712edaeac7bad4b3c19632394d336" kindref="member">View::SetLayoutParams()</ref> to attach parameters to a child view.</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">view.SetLayoutParams(<ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1StackLayoutParams_1a3214d4fdae1bd5152456e4c7a4dc28e8" kindref="member">StackLayoutParams::New</ref>().<ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1StackLayoutParams_1a2c2203ab2405dff78c72b50398978b79" kindref="member">SetWeight</ref>(1.0f));</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
